  "detailed_description": "You need to reach the exit from the dungeon.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThey will try to stop you: walls, patrol droids, turrets, deadly lasers and mechanisms (rotating and moving).<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThey will help you: a shotgun (if you find it), agility and ingenuity. Some objects on the way you can move or destroy. You can use the enemy's forces against them: detonate bombs on the way, rotate combat lasers, tricky use \"friendly fire\". Burning your way to victory!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMany game levels of varying size and difficulty provide a variety of experiences and challenges: somewhere for survival you need dexterity, running and shooting, and somewhere patience and logic.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nClassic first-person view. Controls: WASD + mouse.",
  "about_the_game": "You need to reach the exit from the dungeon.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThey will try to stop you: walls, patrol droids, turrets, deadly lasers and mechanisms (rotating and moving).<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThey will help you: a shotgun (if you find it), agility and ingenuity. Some objects on the way you can move or destroy. You can use the enemy's forces against them: detonate bombs on the way, rotate combat lasers, tricky use \"friendly fire\". Burning your way to victory!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMany game levels of varying size and difficulty provide a variety of experiences and challenges: somewhere for survival you need dexterity, running and shooting, and somewhere patience and logic.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nClassic first-person view. Controls: WASD + mouse.",
